def image_stats(x):
    funs = {k: v for k, v in feature_functions.feature_functions.items()}
    return {k: v(x) for k, v in funs.items()}

def min_max_scale(x, a=0, b=1):
    mn, mx = x.min(), x.max()
    rng = b - a
    out = (x - mn)/(mx-mn)
    return out * rng + a

def get_equalized_stats(image):
    scaled_image = min_max_scale(image, 0, 255).astype('uint8')
    equalized_image = cv2.equalizeHist(scaled_image)
    return image_stats(equalized_image)

    print(im.shape)
    sub_im = im[1000+dx:2000+dx, 1000+dy:2000+dy]
    ax.imshow(sub_im, cmap='jet')
    sub_ims.append(sub_im)
    ax.set_title(name)

bottom, height = 0.1, 0.65
spacing = 0.005

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 6))

ax_hist = fig.add_axes(rect_histy, sharey=ax)

N = 1000
for name, sub_im, dx, dy in zip(names, sub_ims, [-20, 10, 30], [0, 45, 60]):

left, width = 0.1, 0.65
bottom, height = 0.1, 0.65
spacing = 0.005


rect_scatter = [left, bottom, width, height]
rect_histx = [left, bottom + height + spacing, width, 0.2]
rect_histy = [left + width + spacing, bottom, 0.2, height]
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(15, 9))
ax = fig.add_axes(rect_scatter)
ax_hist = fig.add_axes(rect_histy)

N = 1000
sub_profiles = {}
for name, sub_im, dx, dy in zip(names, sub_ims, [-20, 10, 30], [0, 45, 60]):
    x = np.arange(sub_im.shape[1])
    ax_hist = sns.distplot(sub_im[500]-sub_im.min(), vertical=True, hist=False, 
                           kde_kws={'linewidth':3}, ax=ax_hist, )
    sub_profiles[name] = x+dx, sub_im[500]-sub_im.min()
    ax.plot(*sub_profiles[name], label=name, linewidth=3, alpha=.8)
ax.set_ylim(ax_hist.get_ylim())
ax.set_xlim([0, 980])
ax.set_xlabel(r'Length ($\mu m$)')
ax.set_ylabel(r'Height ($\mu m$)')
ax_hist.set_yticks([])
ax.legend()
